Four easy ways to stay safe online
Make sure you can recognize & report phishing
Phishing attacks are a prevalent cybersecurity threat which involve attacks to steal sensitive information like credit card numbers, login credentials, and social security numbers by posing as trustworthy entities. These scams can take many forms, including phishing emails, text message scams, and voice phishing.

